A shekarun 1980s a Karnegie-Holland University, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin fasaha na wucin gadi wanda ya doke dan wasan da ya fi kowa a Amurka, kuma daga baya ya zama babban manajan Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google a China.
