Mai yiwuwa Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron da aka yi a makon nan game da dan takarar kotun koli Burt Kawano, wanda ya zama abin birgewa game da zargin rashin dacewar jima'i da kuma sakamakon dage zaben a majalisar dattijai a mako guda yayin da hukumar FBI ke binciken zargin.
