Gwarzon mai nasara sau uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa ragamar wasan da 'yan Amurka suka ci biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci John Rum da Ian Fulter da ci 2 da 1 a wasannin hudu na kwallon kafa, kuma sun dawo daga baya don doke Fletcher da Rory MacClaroy da ci 4 da 3 a wasannin hudu na wasan, bayan sun rasa wasannin farko guda biyu.
