Sun kusan cin nasara a minti na biyu lokacin da Menga ya tura kwallo ga Scott Patman wanda ya buga ƙofar Alan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya buga ƙwallo da nisa.
Bayan haka, Kagan ya jefa kwallo mai zurfi wanda ya sami Kyaftin Craig Elkett, amma mai kare Alan LaGuardia ya iya buga kwallo kawai a waje da Corra.
Rangers sun yi nasara, amma a wasan karshe, akwai fatan da yawa fiye da imani.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi tunanin cewa ya kamata a yanke masa hukunci bayan an yi karo da shi da Steven Lowe, amma alkalin wasa Steven Thompson ya yi watsi da hukuncin dan wasan na Colombia.
Rangers sun buga kwallo biyu ne kawai a farkon rabin wasan amma mai tsaron gidan Aerox Liam Kelly ya dakatar da saurin LaSanna Coulibaly da kuma Obi Ajaria.
Duk da cewa Livingston ta fara wasa a minti na 34 ba daidai ba ne da yadda aka gudanar da wasan, babu wanda zai musanta cewa sun cancanci hakan, aƙalla saboda aikin da suka yi.
Har ila yau, Rangers sun kasa cin nasara a kan Jacobs mai zurfi.
Scott Artfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe da kwanciyar hankali a kan tura shi zuwa Mango don ƙarewar sauƙi.
Gerard ya yi aiki a rabin lokacin da ya maye gurbin Cullibly da Ryan Kent, kuma musayar ta haifar da tasiri kusan nan take lokacin da mai tsattsauran ra'ayi / flank ya jefa kwallo ga Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya gudu daga layinsa don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ta ci gaba da tilasta wa tawagar da ta halarci wasan ta yi wasa daidai da irin wasan da ta fi so, yayin da Lithgow da Pickett suka ci gaba da aika da dogon harsasai.
Holt's team zai iya karawa da gaba a sauran matakai, amma McGregor ya kasance a kan hanya don hana Jacobs ƙoƙari kafin a cire shi daga kusurwa.
An sake yin wani ƙarar da aka yi wa dan wasan Rangers mai suna Glen Middleton a gaban Jacobs, amma Thompson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
