HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ke da cutar, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya suka ce.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a rabin shekara ta 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda canji ne daga baya.
Kafin yanzu, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wata ganawa da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na zama babbar matsala a cikin al'ummar kasar Sin.
An dakatar da luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma an ce ana nuna wa mutanen da ke da'awar yin jima'i wariya sosai.
Saboda ra'ayoyin da kasar take da shi, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza, za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin kamuwa da cutar na zuwa ne daga rashin amfani da isassun hanyoyin kariya a lokacin jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani daga cikin tawagarta ya leaked bayanai game da Republican sanata kuma ya kare da "dangantaka ƙarya" da kuma "taron makirci"
