Binciken fim din Johnny English 3.0 - Ƙarƙashin ɗan leƙen asiri wanda Rowan Atkinson ya buga
A yau, abu ne da ya zama ruwan dare a neman ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da ra'ayin Birtaniya, kuma hakan ya yi daidai da wannan farfadowar wasan kwaikwayon na Johnny English - wanda ya fara a wani wuri a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya farka zuwa rai a 2011 tare da Johnny English ya dawo.
Shin yin maganganu na wulakanci game da yadda muke da daraja ba zai zama sabon damar fitar da ƙasarmu ba?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English mai cike da idanu da fuska mai laushi ya sami damar sake lalata al'amuran - kuma sunansa ya nuna fiye da komai cewa wannan babban abin dariya ne ga masu kallon fina-finai a ƙasashen da ba sa jin Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, ɗan ɗan ɗan'uwanmu ɗan Ingila, wanda duk da irin kamanninsa na ban mamaki, ya yi kama da Clouseau, ɗan Mr. Bean, da kuma wannan mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa ga waƙar da aka yi wa motocin wuta a lokacin da aka buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Hakanan an samo asali ne daga mai baƙon baƙon baƙon ƙasa wanda Atkinson ya buga a cikin tallan TV da aka manta da Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a bayansa.
Akwai minti daya ko biyu na alheri a cikin sabon juyin Johnny English.
Na fi son inda Johnny English ya zo da jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu sanye da rigar yaƙi ta zamanin da kuma yadda igiyar jirgin take yin sauti a kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana nuna kwarewar sa ta zahiri, amma abin dariya yana jin rauni sosai kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman tunda irin wannan "mai mahimmanci" na finafinan leken asiri kamar 007 da kuma aikin da ba zai yiwu ba yanzu sun haɗa da abun dariya.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar yana magana ne ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a gare ni, abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi na rashin hankali ba su da kyau kuma sun fi mayar da hankali fiye da waƙar fim ɗin Atkinson na Mr. Bean.
Labarin fim din ya fara ne lokacin da babban hatsari ke barazana ga Burtaniya.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asirin Birtaniya, ya bayyana ko wane dan Birtaniya ne a wurin, abin da ya ba babban jami'in tsoro - wani aiki ne da ya yi wa Kevin Aldon wuya.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga firaministan kasar mai girman kai da kuma tsananin damuwa, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken rushewa na asarar shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson yana yin mafi kyau don cika rawar da take da ita kamar Theresa May, amma ba ta da yawa don aiki daga rubutun.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin tsaro sun gaya mata cewa tun da an gano duk wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki, za ta bukaci ta dawo da wani daga aikin.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English mai girman kai a cikin kansa, wanda yanzu yana aiki a matsayin darektan makaranta a wata babbar makaranta, amma yana ba da darussan ba tare da izini ba game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: wasu kyawawan ban dariya a nan, lokacin da Ingilishi ya ba da makarantar sakandare ta makarantar sakandare.
An dawo da Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall don koyarwar gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon mataimakinsa na Baff Mode, wanda Ben Miller ya sake yin.
Buff yanzu mutum ne da ya auri shugaban jirgin ruwan karkashin kasa, a matsayin mai ba da horo mai ban haushi wanda Vicko Pepperdine ta ɗan ɓata.
Sai Batman da Robin na sashen sirrin da ke kula da ayyukanta suka koma aiki, sa'ad da Ophelia Baltoba, mai suna Pam Patel, ta yi wa Olga Kurilenko wasa.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya fada cikin haɗari a ƙarƙashin sihirin mai karamar fasahar zamani wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya - Jason Volta mai ban tsoro a cikin shekarun Jake Lacey.
English da Bouff sun fara Odyssey wanda ya fi wasan kwaikwayo na 'yan wasa biyu: a cikin suturar masu hidima, suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai kyau; suna haifar da tashin hankali yayin da suke kwashe kansu a cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai ban mamaki; kuma English ya sami cikakken rashin tsari a ƙoƙarinsa na amfani da kayan aikin gaskiya don koyon sanin tsarin cikin gidan Volta.
Babu shakka, an yi ƙoƙari sosai don a kai ga wannan jerin, amma duk da irin wannan farin ciki da kuma jin daɗin, yana da kama da talabijin na yara.
