The Labor Party ta musanta ta ke shirya wani shirin ga Birtaniya su yi aiki hudu kwana a mako amma samun biya ga biyar days
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn na duba wani shiri na kawo sauyi inda za a baiwa 'yan Birtaniya aiki kwana hudu a mako - amma za a biya su albashi na kwana biyar.
Rahotanni sun ce jam'iyyar tana son manajojin kamfanoni su ba da kuɗin da aka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha na wucin gadi ga ma'aikata a matsayin karin ranar hutu.
Wato, ma'aikata za su sami hutun mako uku, kuma za su ci gaba da samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin ya dace da shirin tattalin arzikin kamfanin da kuma shirinsa na karkatar da gwamnati don amfanin ma'aikata.
Taron Kungiyoyin kwadago na goyon bayan sauya zuwa mako guda hudu a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su iya more canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labor ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa, "Za a fitar da takardar binciken kafin karshen shekara".
"Ba zai faru ba dare ɗaya, amma aikin kwana huɗu na aiki burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziƙin don amfanin ma'aikata, da kuma dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya".
Jam'iyyar Labor ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi kira ga mako hudu na aiki a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017.
Koyaya, ba a tallafawa burin a halin yanzu ta Jam'iyyar Labor gabaɗaya.
Mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labor ya ce: "Aikin kwana hudu ba manufa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma jam'iyyar ba ta yin la'akari da hakan".
Dan takarar jam'iyyar Labour na zama sakataren kudi, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar a makon da ya gabata don bayyana hangen nesan sa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar janye iko daga masu kula da ba da fuska da masu tsada a kamfanonin samar da kayayyaki.
Shirin dan takarar na ministan kudi ya kuma nuna cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu a kamfanonin ruwa ba za su iya samun cikakken jarin su ba saboda gwamnatin Labor na iya yin "yankan-kashi" bisa ga gano rashin dacewar hali.
Ya kuma amince da cewa akwai shirye-shirye na sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma samar da "kayan aiki masu mahimmanci" don canja wurin kashi 10 cikin 100 na kamfanoni na kamfanoni na kamfanoni ga ma'aikata, wanda zai samar da ribar shekara biyu na har zuwa £500.
