Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, ya yi magana a ranar Lahadi game da karin kudin da aka biya jaridar China ta China Daily, mai suna The Wine Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, inda ya ce kasar Sin ta ki amincewa da hakan.
