An shirya a karbi sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus a 2014 domin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma an dakatar da shi a kalla shekara guda, saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma rage farashin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
Samun Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin sabon layin jirgin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class, yanzu an jinkirta shi zuwa farkon rabin 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito ta ambato wani mai magana da yawun soja.
An shirya jirgin ya shiga cikin jirgin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka shafi samar da kayayyaki sun rufe wannan babban shiri.
Duka jirgi hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class, wanda rundunar sojan ruwa ta yi odar tun 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan na Bremen-class.
