Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da kuma guguwar tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palo na kasar Indonesia, in ji majiyoyin hukuma, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Bala'in ya sa aka katse hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma jami'an agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Dongola, yankin arewacin Fallu, wanda ya fi kusa da tushen sautin 7.5.
A Palo, mutane sama da 16,000 ne suka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Fallu da Dongola, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palo ne babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a 2017, a cewar kimantawa.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwar sa sa'ad da tsunami da girgizar ƙasa suka addabe shi.
Dongola wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yawan jama'a a cikin gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa a cikin lardin, wanda aka kiyasta ya kai mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Babban hanyoyin samun kudin shiga a cikin tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi sune kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin Dongola na bakin teku.
Wani muhimmin tushen samun kudin shiga shine ma'adinan nickel, wanda ya fi yawa a Murvali, a bakin tekun da ke gefen Sulawesi.
Ƙungiyar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi ta damke Fallu da Donggala da ambaliyar tsunami sau da yawa.
