2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a Arewacin Sumatra, a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da wata guguwar tsunami da ta afkawa kasashe 14 inda ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma sama da rabin wadanda suka mutu sun mutu a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
