2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa Kudu Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya fashe a gabar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa wani yanki kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mantuai, kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayin mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa da ta afkawa gundumar Fidi Ghaya a Achha, ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, yayin da mutanen yankin suka tuna da hallaka da ta biyo bayan girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa a 2004.
